---
layout: layouts/page.njk
title: Contact Us
metaTitle: "Schedule a Tour — Contact Azalea Estates in Fayetteville, GA"
description: "Call 770-461-0039 or request a private tour of Azalea Estates in Fayetteville, GA. Our admissions team responds within one business day."
eyebrow: "We’d Love to Hear from You"
pageIntro: "Call, email, or drop us a note — our admissions team responds within one business day."
eleventyComputed:
  pageHero: "{{ images.amenitiesPorch }}"
permalink: /contact/
---

{% from "partials/icons.njk" import icon %}

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="contact-grid">
      <!-- Form -->
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Send a Message</span>
        <h2>Tell us a little about what you&rsquo;re looking for.</h2>
        <p>Whether you&rsquo;re exploring options for yourself or a loved one, we&rsquo;ll help you understand what&rsquo;s available and what it costs &mdash; with no pressure and no sales pitch.</p>

        <form
          name="contact"
          method="POST"
          action="/contact/thanks/"
          data-netlify="true"
          data-netlify-honeypot="bot-field"
          class="form"
        >
          <!-- Required by Netlify to identify the form -->
          <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact">
          <!-- Honeypot: hidden from humans, catches bots -->
          <p style="display:none;">
            <label>Don&rsquo;t fill this out if you&rsquo;re human: <input name="bot-field"></label>
          </p>

          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="first_name">First Name *</label>
              <input type="text" id="first_name" name="first_name" required autocomplete="given-name">
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="last_name">Last Name *</label>
              <input type="text" id="last_name" name="last_name" required autocomplete="family-name">
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="email">Email *</label>
              <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required autocomplete="email">
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="phone">Phone</label>
              <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" autocomplete="tel">
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="relation">This inquiry is for…</label>
              <select id="relation" name="relation">
                <option value="self">Myself</option>
                <option value="parent">A parent</option>
                <option value="spouse">A spouse</option>
                <option value="relative">Another relative</option>
                <option value="professional">A client (I&rsquo;m a professional)</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="interest">Primary interest</label>
              <select id="interest" name="interest">
                <option value="independent">Independent / Retirement Living</option>
                <option value="assisted">Assisted Living</option>
                <option value="respite">Respite / Short-term Care</option>
                <option value="tour">Scheduling a tour</option>
                <option value="other">Something else</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="message">How can we help?</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" placeholder="Tell us a bit about timeline, needs, or any questions you have…"></textarea>
          </div>

          <label class="form-consent">
            <input type="checkbox" name="consent" required>
            <span>I&rsquo;d like to be contacted about Azalea Estates. I understand I can opt out anytime.</span>
          </label>

          <button type="submit" class="btn btn--primary">Send Message</button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <!-- Info card -->
      <aside class="contact-info reveal">
        <h3>Visit or call us.</h3>
        <div class="info-row">
          <div class="info-row__icon">{{ icon('pin', 24) }}</div>
          <div class="info-row__body">
            <strong>Address</strong>
            {{ site.contact.addressLine1 }}<br>
            {{ site.contact.addressLine2 }}<br>
            <a href="{{ site.contact.mapsUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Get directions →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <div class="info-row__icon">{{ icon('phone', 24) }}</div>
          <div class="info-row__body">
            <strong>Phone</strong>
            <a href="tel:{{ site.contact.phoneRaw }}">{{ site.contact.phone }}</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <div class="info-row__icon">{{ icon('mail', 24) }}</div>
          <div class="info-row__body">
            <strong>Email</strong>
            <a href="mailto:{{ site.contact.email }}">{{ site.contact.email }}</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <div class="info-row__icon">{{ icon('clock', 24) }}</div>
          <div class="info-row__body">
            <strong>Tour Hours</strong>
            Monday – Friday, 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM<br>
            Saturday by appointment
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- MAP EMBED -->
<!-- SERVICE AREA -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="intro-split">
      <div class="intro-split__body reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Who We Serve</span>
        <h2>Proudly serving Fayette County and the Southern Crescent since 1993.</h2>
        <p class="lead">Azalea Estates of Fayetteville is the senior living community of choice for families throughout Fayette County &mdash; and the surrounding region.</p>
        <p>Located just off Highway 54 in the heart of Fayetteville, Georgia, we are convenient to residents and families from Peachtree City, Tyrone, Brooks, Woolsey, Senoia, Newnan, and the greater Atlanta metro area. Our campus at 105 Autumn Glen Circle is easy to reach, easy to navigate, and easy to call home.</p>
        <p>If you are exploring senior living options for yourself or a loved one anywhere in the Southern Crescent region &mdash; from Fayette County south to Coweta County or east to Clayton County &mdash; we would be honored to be considered.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="intro-split__body reveal">
        <h3 style="font-size:1.1rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Communities we serve</h3>
        <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--space-2) var(--space-5);">
          {% set cities = ["Fayetteville, GA", "Peachtree City, GA", "Tyrone, GA", "Brooks, GA", "Woolsey, GA", "Senoia, GA", "Newnan, GA", "Union City, GA", "Jonesboro, GA", "McDonough, GA", "Fairburn, GA", "Palmetto, GA"] %}
          {% for city in cities %}
            <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:var(--space-2); font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--c-ink-soft);">
              <span style="color:var(--c-forest);">{{ icon('pin', 14) }}</span> {{ city }}
            </div>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- VIRTUAL TOUR -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="intro-split">
      <div class="intro-split__body reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Can&rsquo;t Visit in Person Yet?</span>
        <h2>Take our 360&deg; virtual tour first.</h2>
        <p class="lead">Explore every room, hallway, and outdoor space at Azalea Estates from your phone or computer &mdash; any time, at your own pace.</p>
        <p>Our interactive virtual tour is especially useful for out-of-town family members researching options for a loved one. Walk the dining room, peek into a private suite, see the wellness center &mdash; then call us with your questions.</p>
        <a href="/gallery/" class="btn btn--ghost">Open full-screen virtual tour</a>
      </div>
      <div class="intro-split__media reveal">
        <div class="virtual-tour virtual-tour--square">
          <iframe
            src="https://tourmkr.com/F1NLCFWPFI/32620506p&amp;194.98h&amp;88.35t"
            title="Azalea Estates of Fayetteville &mdash; Interactive 360&deg; Virtual Tour"
            allowfullscreen
            loading="lazy">
          </iframe>
        </div>
        <p class="virtual-tour__hint">Drag to look around &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; Pinch or scroll to zoom</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="directions" class="section section--cream">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-heading reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Map &amp; Directions</span>
      <h2>Easy to find, easy to visit.</h2>
      <p>We&rsquo;re just off Highway 54 in the center of Fayetteville, on Autumn Glen Circle &mdash; about 13 miles from Peachtree City and 30 miles south of Atlanta.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden; box-shadow: var(--shadow); aspect-ratio: 16/7;">
      <iframe
        src="https://www.google.com/maps?q=105+Autumn+Glen+Cir+Fayetteville+GA+30215&output=embed"
        title="Map showing Azalea Estates of Fayetteville"
        width="100%" height="100%" style="border:0;"
        loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
        allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section id="faq" class="section">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <div class="section-heading reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Common Questions</span>
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    </div>

    <details class="reveal" style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-line); padding: var(--space-4) 0;">
      <summary style="cursor:pointer; font-weight:600; font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.2rem;">Who is Assisted Living designed for?</summary>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-3);">It&rsquo;s for individuals who need some assistance with activities of daily living &mdash; bathing, dressing, medication reminders, mobility, or transportation &mdash; while still maintaining as much independence as possible. Our licensed RN and LPN are on staff to support each resident&rsquo;s individual plan.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="reveal" style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-line); padding: var(--space-4) 0;">
      <summary style="cursor:pointer; font-weight:600; font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.2rem;">What&rsquo;s included in the monthly rate?</summary>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-3);">All utilities and cable (except telephone), complete building WiFi, three daily chef-prepared meals, weekly housekeeping and linen service, emergency response systems, and access to all wellness, social, and community amenities. Personal care services are added in flexible tiers based on need.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="reveal" style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-line); padding: var(--space-4) 0;">
      <summary style="cursor:pointer; font-weight:600; font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.2rem;">Can you help with long-term care insurance?</summary>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-3);">Yes. Our admissions team is experienced in helping residents both apply for and submit monthly forms for long-term care insurance. Many residents have a substantial portion of their costs covered this way.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="reveal" style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-line); padding: var(--space-4) 0;">
      <summary style="cursor:pointer; font-weight:600; font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.2rem;">Are assisted living fees tax deductible?</summary>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-3);">In many circumstances, yes. We can share general guidance and resources on medical-expense deductibility. We always recommend confirming with your accountant or tax advisor for your specific situation.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="reveal" style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-line); padding: var(--space-4) 0;">
      <summary style="cursor:pointer; font-weight:600; font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.2rem;">Are pets allowed?</summary>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-3);">Absolutely. Small pets are very welcome at Azalea Estates &mdash; we love having them in our community.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="reveal" style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-line); padding: var(--space-4) 0;">
      <summary style="cursor:pointer; font-weight:600; font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.2rem;">How do I schedule a tour?</summary>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-3);">Call us at <a href="tel:{{ site.contact.phoneRaw }}">{{ site.contact.phone }}</a>, send a message through the form above, or simply drop by during tour hours. We&rsquo;ll show you the campus, available suites, and answer every question.</p>
    </details>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CAREERS -->
<section id="careers" class="section section--ink">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="intro-split">
      <div class="intro-split__body reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--c-accent-soft);">Careers at Azalea Estates</span>
        <h2>Join a team people stay with for years.</h2>
        <p class="lead" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);">Azalea Estates is known for the longevity of its staff &mdash; because when you love the work and the people, you tend to stay. If that sounds like where you want to be, we&rsquo;d love to talk.</p>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);">We hire across all departments: nursing and resident care, dining and culinary, wellness and activities, housekeeping, maintenance, and administration. No open position listed? Send a general inquiry anyway &mdash; we accept r&eacute;sum&eacute;s year-round.</p>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);">Visit our <a href="/team/" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);">Our Team page</a> to learn more about the people you&rsquo;d be working alongside.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="intro-split__body reveal" style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap: var(--space-4);">
        <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: var(--space-5);">
          <h3 style="color: var(--c-cream); font-size:1.2rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-3);">What We Offer</h3>
          <ul style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.80); padding-left: var(--space-5); line-height:2.1;">
            <li>Meaningful daily work with real human impact</li>
            <li>Stable, long-tenured team environment</li>
            <li>Competitive pay and scheduling flexibility</li>
            <li>On-campus dining for all staff</li>
            <li>Genuine recognition and a culture of care</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <a href="mailto:{{ site.contact.email }}?subject=Careers+Inquiry+%E2%80%94+Azalea+Estates"
           class="btn btn--primary"
           style="align-self: flex-start;">
          Send Your R&eacute;sum&eacute;
        </a>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.50); font-size:0.875rem;">
          Email to <a href="mailto:{{ site.contact.email }}" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.70);">{{ site.contact.email }}</a> with subject &ldquo;Careers Inquiry&rdquo; and a note about the role(s) you&rsquo;re interested in.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
